.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis
2 different pets are kept: frog, guinea-pig
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is the person driving the quad-bike##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |      2      |
| Flower       | amaryllis | balloon-flower |
| Pet         | frog      | guinea-pig  |
| Transport   | motorbike | quad-bike   |

