The people prefer 2 different music-genres: indie, punk
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, biathlon
1. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | indie       | punk     |
| Sport     | biathlon       | golf     |

