2 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, dannemann
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the pall-mall-smoker is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | rock          |
| Cigar     | dannemann     | pall-mall           |

